      "content": "it wasn't \"contained within minutes\" though. it was open for three days. if someone asks specifically how many days the bucket was exposed, we can't really say it was minutes without a direct lie. is there any other angle we can take that keeps the reputation intact without having to claim things happened much faster than they actually did?",
